  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Self-Delusion</strong> is a first-person survival horror. The game based on an original setting of grim fairy tales and myths. You will face evil creatures such as: <i>Kolobok</i>, <i>Leshy</i>, <i>Boggart</i>, <i>Lapot</i> and other mystical characters.<br>The danger will await you everywhere: in a mystery house full of evil creatures, in an old school or in an abandoned village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/1674f363add31e4209a4a5e7b621c1cf.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=144 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Horror in the original setting</strong><br>Monsters unique to the horror genre, only found in fairytales and folklore up 'til now.<br></li><li><strong>Opponents with unique abilities and behavior pattern</strong><br>Find your survival strategy based on the behavior of the monsters and the environment.<br></li><li><strong>Atmosphere</strong><br>Tense atmosphere complete with jump scares and heart hammering races to beat the clock. <br></li><li><strong>Exploring</strong><br>Explore a strange village house and other locations. Can you uncover the secrets of these places?<br></li><li><strong>Different endings</strong><br>Alternate endings that shed new insight on the story and add hours of re-playability. <br></li><li><strong>Story</strong><br>An enthralling storyline that will leave you gasping in shock and on the edge of your seat. <br></li><li><strong>Complexity</strong><br>Choose the game difficulty that suits you best, depending on your skills.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you could have guessed the main goal is <strong>survive</strong>. Sounds pretty easy but do not delude yourself. The situation will change every second and the monsters have no mercy for you.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/5a775c02c5c93bc56e16f5ccdf2e6ddb.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Self-Delusion</strong> is a first-person survival horror. The game based on an original setting of grim fairy tales and myths. You will face evil creatures such as: <i>Kolobok</i>, <i>Leshy</i>, <i>Boggart</i>, <i>Lapot</i> and other mystical characters.<br>The danger will await you everywhere: in a mystery house full of evil creatures, in an old school or in an abandoned village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/c9514f4e8cb57d6a9e613fda74c99679.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/1674f363add31e4209a4a5e7b621c1cf.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=144 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Horror in the original setting</strong><br>Monsters unique to the horror genre, only found in fairytales and folklore up 'til now.<br></li><li><strong>Opponents with unique abilities and behavior pattern</strong><br>Find your survival strategy based on the behavior of the monsters and the environment.<br></li><li><strong>Atmosphere</strong><br>Tense atmosphere complete with jump scares and heart hammering races to beat the clock. <br></li><li><strong>Exploring</strong><br>Explore a strange village house and other locations. Can you uncover the secrets of these places?<br></li><li><strong>Different endings</strong><br>Alternate endings that shed new insight on the story and add hours of re-playability. <br></li><li><strong>Story</strong><br>An enthralling storyline that will leave you gasping in shock and on the edge of your seat. <br></li><li><strong>Complexity</strong><br>Choose the game difficulty that suits you best, depending on your skills.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.poster.avif?t=1702571399\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.webm?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1590190/extras/417516edb47c7d87e84c10248b46ff9b.mp4?t=1702571399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you could have guessed the main goal is <strong>survive</strong>. Sounds pretty easy but do not delude yourself. The situation will change every second and the monsters have no mercy for you.",
